levision facility)|dock10 studios]], [[Salford]]<ref name=heralditv>{{cite news |last1=Mcilkenny |first1=Stephen |title=Everything you need to know about Johnson v Corbyn: The ITV Debate |url=https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/18045174.johnson-v-corbyn-itv-debate---everything-need-know/ |accessdate=19 November 2019 |work=HeraldScotland |date=19 November 2019}}</ref>\n| UK\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |7.34\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Boris Johnson|Johnson]]}}}}\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Jeremy Corbyn|Corbyn]]}}}}\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n|-\n| 22 November<ref name=\"Sheffield\">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2019/nov/22/question-time-leaders-special-who-won-johnson-corbyn-swinson-sturgeon|title=BBC Question Time leaders special: who came out on top?|last=Walker|first=Peter|date=22 November 2019|work=The Guardian|access-date=25 November 2019|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077}}</ref>\n|[[BBC]]<br />(''[[Question Time (TV programme)|Question Time]]'')\n|[[Octagon Centre]], [[Sheffield]]<ref name=\"OctagonCentre\">{{cite news |last1=O'Callaghan |first1=Niall |title=Octagon to host party leaders BBC Question Time special tomorrow {{!}} Forge |url=http://forgetoday.com/2019/11/21/octagon-to-host-party-leaders-bbc-question-time-special-tomorrow/ |accessdate=30 November 2019 |work=Forge Today |publisher=University of Sheffield's Students Union |date=21 November 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"Sheffield\" />\n| UK\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |4.62\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Boris Johnson|Johnson]]}}}}\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Jeremy Corbyn|Corbyn]]}}}}\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Nicola Sturgeon|S