d away from climate debate |url=https://www.eveningexpress.co.uk/news/uk/tories-clash-with-channel-4-as-michael-gove-turned-away-from-climate-debate/ |accessdate=30 November 2019 |work=Evening Express |agency=Press Association |date=29 November 2019 |quote=Channel 4 News' General Election climate debate at ITN Studios in Holborn, central London}}</ref>\n| UK\n| align=\"center\" <----DK---- >{{TBA}}\n|{{No|'''A'''{{refn|group=n|Channel 4 described this as a leaders-only debate, and refused to accept [[Michael Gove]] as substitute.<ref>{{cite tweet|user=bendepear|last=de Pear|first=Ben|number=1200182009735319552|title=It was kind of @michaelgove to offer himself on C4News instead of @BorisJohnson & we always welcome him. However, as made clear, as he isn't the leader of the Conservatives his participation was not required at tonight's #climatedebate- which was strictly for party leaders only.|date=28 November 2019|accessdate=29 November 2019}}</ref>}}<br>{{small|[[Boris Johnson|Johnson]]}}}}\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Jeremy Corbyn|Corbyn]]}}}}\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Nicola Sturgeon|Sturgeon]]}}}} \n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Jo Swinson|Swinson]]}}}}\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Adam Price|Price]]}}}}\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Si\u00e2n Berry|Berry]]}}}}\n| {{No|'''A'''<br>{{small|[[Nigel Farage|Farage]]}}}}\n|-\n| 29 November<ref>{{cite tweet|user=BBCNewsPR|author=BBC News Press Team|number=1199669183837081601|title=Here is the line-up for The BBC Election Debate on Friday #GE2019|date=27 November 2019|accessdate=27 November 2019}}</ref>\n| [[BBC]]\n| [[Senedd building|Senedd]], [[Cardiff]]<ref name=\"29NovSenedd\">{{cite web |last1=Mosalski |first1=Ruth |title=Rate the political parties in the BBC General Election debate in Cardiff |url=https://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/politics/rate-political-parties-bbc-general-17340340 |website=Wales Online |accessdate=30 November 2019 |date=29 November 2019}}</ref>\n| UK\n| align=\"center\" <----DK---- >{{TBA}}