19-50681321 |accessdate=6 December 2019 |date=6 December 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/live/2019/dec/06/general-election-boris-johnson-jeremy-corbyn-final-tv-debate-live-news |title=BBC debate: Johnson and Corbyn clash over Brexit, NHS and racist language \u2013 as it happened |date=7 December 2019 |work=The Guardian |accessdate=17 December 2019}}</ref>\t\n| UK\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |4.42\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Boris Johnson|Johnson]]}}}}\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Jeremy Corbyn|Corbyn]]}}}}\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n|-\n| 8 December<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.pressgazette.co.uk/channel-4-cancels-leaders-debate-over-boris-johnson-no-show/|title=Channel 4 cancels leaders' debate over Boris Johnson no-show|last=Mayhew|first=Freddy|date=22 November 2019|work=Press Gazette|accessdate=23 November 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.channel4.com/programmes/britain-decides-everything-but-brexit-debate|title=Britain Decides: Everything But Brexit Debate|work=Channel 4|accessdate=1 December 2019}}</ref>\n|[[Channel 4]] <br />''(everything but Brexit)''\n| [[Leeds Beckett University]], [[Leeds]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.leeds-live.co.uk/news/leeds-news/live-updates-channel-4-host-17384667|title=Channel 4 General Election debate in Leeds - as it happened|first1=Kristian|last1=Johnson|first2=Ian|last2=Hughes|date=9 December 2019|website=leedslive}}</ref>\n| UK\n| align=\"center\" <----DK---- >{{TBA}}\n| {{No|'''A'''<br>}}\n| style=\"background:#D0F0C0; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''S'''<br>{{small|[[Angela Rayner|Rayner]]}}\n| style=\"background:#D