| style=\"background:#D0F0C0; color:black; text-align:center;\" | '''S'''<br>{{small|[[Nia Griffith|Griffith]]}}\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| {{Yes|'''P'''<br>{{small|[[Jane Dodds|Dodds]]}}}}\n| style=\"background:#D0F0C0; color:black; text-align:center;\" | '''S'''<br>{{small|[[Liz Saville Roberts|Saville Roberts]]}}\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#D0F0C0; color:black; text-align:center;\" | '''S'''<br>{{small|[[James Wells (British politician)|Wells]]}}\n|-\n| 28 November<br />(cancelled)<ref name=\"climate\"/>\n| <s>[[Sky News]]</s>\n| <s>N/A</s>\n| <s>UK</s>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<s>N/A</s>\n| {{Yes-No|'''N'''<br>{{small|[[Boris Johnson|Johnson]]}}}}\n| {{Yes-No|'''N'''<br>{{small|[[Jeremy Corbyn|Corbyn]]}}}}\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| {{Yes-No|'''N'''<br>{{small|[[Jo Swinson|Swinson]]}}}}\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n| style=\"background:#A2B2C2; color:black; text-align:center;\" |'''NI'''\n|-\n| 28 November<ref>{{cite tweet |user=bendepear |last=de Pear |first=Ben |number=1199015981198331904 |title=This Thursday 28th @Channel4News will devote its hour @7 to debate climate change. Thus far Jeremy Corbyn, Nicola Sturgeon, Jo Swinson & Sian Berry have confirmed. The invitation remains open to @BorisJohnson & @Nigel_Farage but this debate will go ahead with or without them |date=25 November 2019 |accessdate=25 November 2019}}</ref>\n|[[Channel 4]]<br />(''climate and nature'')\n| [[ITN#Studios at ITN|ITN Headquarters]], [[London]]<ref name=\"ch4studioinfo\">{{cite news |title=Tories clash with Channel 4 as Michael Gove turned away from climate debate |url=https://www.eveningexpress.co.uk/news/uk/tories-clash-with-channel-4-as-michael-gove-turned-away-from-climate-debate/