l|as of 12 December 2019}}\n! style=\"vertical-align:top;\" | Election Maps UK<ref>{{cite tweet |title=#GE2019 Nowcast (12th Dec): |number=1205161747600019456 |user=ElectionMapsUK |date=December 12, 2019 |accessdate=December 12, 2019}}</ref><br />{{small|as of 12 December 2019}}\n! style=\"vertical-align:top;\" | Elections Etc.<ref>{{cite web |title=Final combined forecast for the 2019 General Election |url=https://electionsetc.com/2019/12/12/final-combined-forecast-for-the-2019-general-election/#more-2658 |website=Elections Etc |accessdate=December 12, 2019 |date=12 December 2019}}</ref><br />{{small|as of 12 December 2019}}\n! style=\"vertical-align:top;\" | UK-Elect<ref>{{cite web |title=UK-Elect General Election Forecast, December 11th 2019 |url=https://www.ukelect.co.uk/HTML/forecasts/20191211ForecastUK.html |website=UK-Elect |accessdate=December 11, 2019}}</ref><br />{{small|as of 11 December 2019}}\n|-\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservatives]]\n| {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | {{center|339}}\n| {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | {{center|351}}\n| {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | {{center|344}}\n| {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | {{center|341}}\n| {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | {{center|348}}\n|-\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Labour Party (UK)|Labour Party]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 231\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 224\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 223\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 224\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 217\n|-\n| bgcolor=\"{{Scottish National Party/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Scottish National Party|SNP]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 41\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 41\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 45\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 43\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 44\n|-\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Democrats (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Liberal Democrats (UK)|Liberal Democrats]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 15\n