d]]</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 7\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{Percentage|7|650|1|pad=yes}}\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|7|650|hex={{Sinn F\u00e9in/meta/color}}}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 181,853\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 0.6%\n| {{percentage bar|0.6||c={{Sinn F\u00e9in/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Plaid Cymru/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Plaid Cymru]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Adam Price]]</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 4\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{Percentage|4|650|1|pad=yes}}\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|4|650|hex={{Plaid Cymru/meta/color}}}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 153,265\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 0.5%\n| {{percentage bar|0.5||c={{Plaid Cymru/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Social Democratic and Labour Party]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Colum Eastwood]]</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 2\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{Percentage|2|650|1|pad=yes}}\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|2|650|hex={{Green Party of England and Wales/meta/color}}}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 118,737 \n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 0.4%\n| {{percentage bar|0.4||c={{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Green Party of England and Wales/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Green Party of England and Wales]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Jonathan Bartley]]<br />[[Si\u00e2n Berry]]</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{Percentage|1|650|1|pad=yes}}\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|1|650|hex={{Green Party of England and Wales/meta/color}}}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 835,579 \n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 2.7%\n| {{percentage bar|2.7||c={{Green Party of England and Wales/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Alliance Party of Northern Ireland/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Alliance Party of Northern Ireland]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Naomi Long]]</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{Percentage|1|650|1|pad=yes}}\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|1|650|hex={{Green Party of England and Wales/meta/color}}}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 134,115 \n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 0.4%\n| {{percentage bar|0.4||c={{Alliance Party of Northern Ireland/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Speaker of the British House of Commons/meta/color}};\" |\n| {{n/a|[[Speaker of the House of Commons (United Kingdom)|Speaker]]}}\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Lindsay Hoyle]]</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{Percentage|1|650|1|pad=yes}}\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|1|650|hex={{Speaker of the British House of Commons/meta/color}}}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 26,831\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 0.1%\n| {{percentage bar|0.1||c={{Speaker of the British House of Commons/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|}\n\n===Full results===\n{{2019 United Kingdom parliamentary election}}\n{{bar box\n|title=Vote share\n|titlebar=#ddd\n|width=600px\n|barwidth=410px\n|bars=\n{{bar percent|'''Conservative'''|{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}|43.6}} <!-- Parliament itself lists the Speaker separately; see note above by the Conservative seat tally in the main infobox -->\n{{bar percent|Labour|{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}|32.2}}\n{{bar percent|Liberal Democrat|{{Liberal De