ber |website=Hansard 1803\u20132005 |publisher=UK Parliament |accessdate=26 November 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=2 style=\"background-color: {{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| rowspan=2 | [[File:No image.svg|75px]]\n| rowspan=2 | [[Fred Peart, Baron Peart|<small>The Right Honourable</small><br>'''Fred Peart''']]<br><small>MP for [[Workington (UK Parliament constituency)|Workington]]<br>(1914\u20131988)</small>\n| rowspan=2 | <small>5 March</small><br>1974\n| rowspan=2 | <small>10 September</small><br>1976\n| rowspan=2 {{Party shading/Labour}} | [[Labour Party (UK)|Labour]]\n| {{Party shading/Labour}} | [[Labour government, 1974\u20131979|Wilson<br><small>(III & IV)</small>]]\n| rowspan=2 |\n|-\n| rowspan=2 {{Party shading/Labour}} | [[Labour government, 1974\u20131979|Callaghan]]\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[File:No image.svg|75px]]\n| [[John Silkin|<small>The Right Honourable</small><br>'''John Silkin''']]<br><small>MP for [[Worcester (UK Parliament constituency)|Worcester]]<br>(1923\u20131987)</small>\n| <small>10 September</small><br>1976\n| <small>4 May</small><br>1979\n| {{Party shading/Labour}} | [[Labour Party (UK)|Labour]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parliament.uk/biographies/Commons/member/1335 |title=Rt Hon John Silkin |publisher=UK Parliament |accessdate=24 November 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[File:No image.svg|75px]]\n| [[Peter Walker, Baron Walker of Worcester|<small>The Right Honourable</small><br>'''Peter Walker'''<br><small>MBE</small>]]<br><small>MP for [[Worcester (UK Parliament constituency)|Worcester]]<br>(1932\u20132010)</small>\n| <small>5 May</small><br>1979\n| <small>11 June</small><br>1983\n| {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | [[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservative]]\n| {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | [[First Thatcher ministry|Thatcher I]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parliament.uk/biographies/Lords/member/