d-jopling/883 |title=Lord Jopling |publisher=UK Parliament |accessdate=24 November 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[File:official portrait of Lord MacGregor of Pulham Market crop 2.jpg|75px]]\n| [[John MacGregor, Baron MacGregor of Pulham Market|<small>The Right Honourable</small><br>'''John MacGregor'''<br><small>OBE</small>]]<br><small>MP for [[South Norfolk (UK Parliament constituency)|South Norfolk]]<br>(1937\u2013)</small>\n| <small>13 June</small><br>1987\n| <small>24 July</small><br>1989\n| {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | [[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservative]]\n| rowspan=2 {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | [[Third Thatcher ministry|Thatcher III]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.parliament.uk/biographies/lords/lord-macgregor-of-pulham-market/131 |title=Lord MacGregor of Pulham Market |publisher=UK Parliament |accessdate=24 November 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=3 style=\"background-color: {{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| rowspan=3 | [[File:John Gummer 2006-03-01.jpg|75px]]\n| rowspan=3 | [[John Gummer|<small>The Right Honourable</small><br>'''John Gummer''']]<br><small>MP for [[Suffolk Coastal (UK Parliament constituency)|Suffolk Coastal]]<br>(1939\u2013)</small>\n| rowspan=3 | <small>24 July</small><br>1989\n| rowspan=3 | <small>27 May</small><br>1993\n| rowspan=3 {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | [[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservative]]\n| rowspan=3 | <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parliament.uk/biographies/lords/lord-deben/4154 |title=Lord Deben |publisher=UK Parliament |accessdate=24 November 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | [[First Major ministry|Major I]]\n|-\n| rowspan=4 {{Party shading/Conservative (UK)}} | [[Second Major ministry|Major II]]\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[File:Official portrait of Baroness Shephard of Northwold crop 2.jpg|75px]]\n| [[Gillian Shephard|<small>The Right Honou